MANUAL INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
===========================

A rough guide to setting up Dazibao.

Install cups-pdf on your machine
$ sudo apt-get install cups-pdf

Install imagemagick on your machine
$ sudo apt-get install imagemagick

Overwrite /etc/cups/cups-pdf.conf with the supplied file 
$ cp cups-pdf.conf /etc/cups/

Create the directory /var/dazibao/images
$ mkdir -p /var/dazibao/images

Serve the contents of /var/dazibao over HTTP on port 4555
(e.g. install nginx and use the supplied configuration files)

Test it by accessing your machine over HTTP on port 4555.

